kgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe179644909c9e74183426ab8be70c8a0cac5e24","tid":858624,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去查詢下都得<br />\n<br />\nenquiry@immd.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b8b8a27fc8d207f0a186e7adbd3721e014d804","tid":858624,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:04:15.000Z","msg":"每個case都要分開處理喎<br />\n<br />\n我有唔知咪去問囉<br />\n<br />\n應該唔犯法嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a99a30728d99e2c035c1a4d9587ebe87d9f1fdf","tid":858624,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"俾個例子你地, send去 enquiry@immd.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa11653e349785362024f6c8e8151c79116af9f7","tid":858624,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:59:20.000Z","msg":"大家話有無得諗？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3d35845f7fde93f63ea741a88350b67a928bc9","tid":858624,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"增加佢行政成本 一定要覆你<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多日常生活細節係可以向各政府部門查詢<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要一人一日一email<br />\n<br />\n問清楚啲係市民嘅權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}